{
  "name": "Haunt Path",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 1st level, the wraith chooses a haunt path. Once selected, this choice cannot be changed. Path skills are always class skills for wraiths with that path.</p>\n<p>At 1st level, each path grants the listed path sphere, or a talent from that sphere if it is already possessed, as a bonus magic talent and uses his class level as his caster level with the path sphere. This stacks normally with caster levels gained from other sources.</p>\n<p>At 2nd level, the wraith gains a path possession, granting additional options for his possession ability.</p>\n<p>At 4th level, the wraith gains an insight bonus to the listed skill equal to half his class level.</p>\n<p>At 8th level, the wraith gains an improved path possession, granting further options to his possession ability.</p>\n<p>At 14th level, the wraith gains a greater path possession, granting a final expansion of options to his possession ability.</p>\n",
